B2B_Subscription_BasicKeyFeature:
Key features and services: 

* Flexible PDF creation and markup    

* Easy markup and collaboration on any web or iOS device, with unlimited cloud storage

* Access to partner-built integrations 

* Access to free Bluebeam University courses and comprehensive technical support
B2B_Subscription_CoreKeyFeature:
All Basics features and services, plus: 

* Real-time collaboration with Studio 
in Revu    

* Robust takeoff tools, document comparison and specialty markups 

* Punch, RFIs and submittal management on any web or 
iOS device 

* Unlimited storage as part of Bluebeam Cloud and Studio           

* Access to geolocational insights
B2B_Subscription_CompleteKeyFeature:
All Core features and services, plus: 

* Advanced measurement tools, including volume, formulas and Dynamic Fill for more accurate, 
faster takeoffs     

* Advanced batch automation tools, including Batch Link® and Batch Sign & Seal to increase project efficiency 

* Advanced reporting on markups for improved tracking and accountability
B2B_BasicsProductDescriptions:
Essential tools for marking up and managing your AECO office and project documents​. 

Includes: Revu lite, Bluebeam Cloud Markup Editor
B2B_CoreProductDescriptions:
Comprehensive tools for managing and collaborating on small- and mid-sized AECO projects​. 


Includes: Revu standard, Bluebeam Cloud Markup Editor and Field Tools
B2B_CompleteProductDescriptions:
Everything you need to manage and optimize complex AECO projects at scale​.  

Includes: Revu advanced, Bluebeam Cloud Markup Editor and Field Tools
